ues and multi-standards systems optimization<br \\/>Management of the reconfigurability<br \\/>Management of the Cognitive Radio cycle<br \\/>High level modeling for cognitive radio design<br \\/>Implementation on heterogeneous platforms (FPGA, DSP)<br \\/>Validation on platforms (USRP, SDR2000, ...)<\\/li><\\/ul><p><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.rennes.supelec.fr\\/ren\\/rd\\/scee\\/themes\\/scee_capteurs.en.html\\">Smart sensors of our 3 layers model<\\/a><\\/p><ul><li>Layer 3 : <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.rennes.supelec.fr\\/ren\\/rd\\/scee\\/themes\\/scee_ti.html\\">Face analysis and synthesis<\\/a><br \\/>Layer 2 : <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.rennes.supelec.fr\\/ren\\/rd\\/scee\\/themes\\/scee_ti.html\\">Blind standards recognition sensor, ...<\\/a><br \\/>Layer 1 : <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.rennes.supelec.fr\\/ren\\/rd\\/scee\\/themes\\/scee_ti.html\\">Spectrum holes detector in SISO and MIMO context, ...<\\/a><\\/li><\\/ul>","drop_cap":"yes","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Roboto"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false}]'),
