(47, 1, '2017-05-02 17:12:20', '2017-05-02 15:12:20', '<table border="2">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr align="center">\r\n<td>  <a href="http://www.rennes.supelec.fr/ren/fi/seri/ftp/presentation_SERI_juin2016.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><b>Full presentation</b> </a>\r\n(pdf, june 2016)</td>\r\n<td>  <a href="http://www.rennes.supelec.fr/ren/fi/seri/ftp/Relance_SERI_oct2010.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><b>Domains &amp; Jobs</b> </a>\r\n(pdf, oct. 2010)</td>\r\n<td>  <a href="http://www.rennes.supelec.fr/ren/fi/seri/projets_SERI.html" target="_top"><b>Projects &amp; Lab Works</b> </a>\r\n(html)</td>\r\n<td>  <a href="http://www.rennes.supelec.fr/ren/fi/seri/ftp/CEI_Plaq2015_SERI.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><b>Industrial Study presentation</b> </a>\r\n(pdf, june 2015)</td>\r\n<td>  <a href="https://freemove.centralesupelec.fr/en/electronic-network-and-image-systems.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><b>Diplôme de Spécialisation</b>\r\n<img src="http://www.rennes.supelec.fr/ren/fi/seri/logos/FreeMoov.jpg" width="80" height="10" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nThe aim of the 3rd Year Major SERI, specialized in “Electronic Systems, Networks &amp; Images” is to train highly skilled engineers in electronic systems, especially for nomad and mobile applications.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/MajorPresentation1.png" sizes="(max-width: 634px) 100vw, 634px" srcset="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/MajorPresentation1.png 634w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/MajorPresentation1-300x153.png 300w" alt="" width="634" height="323" />\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Signal processing with case studies for multimedia, digital communications and networks.</li>\r\n 	<li>Design of analog and digital electronics : define, in good adequacy between technology and applications, architecture of systems ; main performance targets are speed, cost, power consumption, integration density.</li>\r\n 	<li>Design management including methods and tools, necessary for engineers to specify, realize, test and qualify industrial products.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nA set of topical seminars on state of the art applications, delivered by industrialists, is used to illustrate the use of these techniques in the economic world.\r\n\r\nThe training is thus designed so as to allow the students to master methods and tools used in current developments, but also to be a driving force for future evolutions in a large industry spectrum.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Program of Major SERI (2013/2014)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.rennes.supelec.fr/ren/fi/seri/ftp/Programme_SERI2014_Anglais.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Core curriculum modules</a> (pdf file)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Lab Works</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Final Training</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Programs of Minor Courses on Rennes Campus</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Planning &amp; abstracts of <a href="http://www.rennes.supelec.fr/ren/fi/mineures_ren.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Minor</a> Courses on Rennes Campus</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.rennes.supelec.fr/ren/fi/seri/ftp/prog_mineures-niveau3-rennes_5juillet2010.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Electronics &amp; Telecom</a> (Floor 3 on Rennes Campus ; fichier PDF)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="justify"></p>', 'Major SERI', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'signal-processing', '', '', '2017-05-11 12:26:08', '2017-05-11 10:26:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=47', 0, 'page', '', 0),
