ages dans une séquence d’images vidéo</a> (Renaud <a href="http://www.rennes.supelec.fr/ren/perso/rseguier" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Séguier</a>)\r\n<h3><strong>1991</strong></h3>\r\n<a href="http://www.rennes.supelec.fr/ren/rd/scee/theses/mao_1991.html">Processeurs à tolérance de fautes</a> (Zhigang MAO)\r\n<h3><b>1988</b></h3>\r\n<a href="http://www.rennes.supelec.fr/ren/rd/scee/theses/dong_1988.html">Étude et réalisation d’un convertisseur analogique-numérique rapide en technologie CMOS</a> (Yan Hua DONG)\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.rennes.supelec.fr/ren/rd/scee/theses/weiss_1988.html">Amélioration de l’aspect subjectif des images de télévision</a> (Jacques <a href="http://www.rennes.supelec.fr/ren/perso/jweiss" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Weiss </a>)\r\nConception d’un terminal de manipulation de documents en mode mixte – Structuration et transfert de documents (Shaofeng Li)', 'Thesis Defended', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '185-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-11 14:06:06', '2017-05-11 12:06:06', '', 185, 'http://localhost/wordpress/index.php/2017/05/11/185-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(832, 1, '2017-05-11 14:18:17', '2017-05-11 12:18:17', 'The TestBed is....\r\n<figure><img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/20170503_115328-n7z5l169qt5cvraixiopfdmdbwl7a99wy19370s5uo.jpg" alt="This is the monitor" /></figure>\r\n<figure><img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/20170503_115508-n7z5lbihtzjifgvi955lot0fv568mxeyngffh2cty8.jpg" alt="The TestBed''s Setup" /></figure>\r\n<figure><img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/20170503_115443-n7z5l8oz9hfngmzlplxpzbq22zk4zu3rn2gz18h0gw.jpg" alt="The TestBed''s Setup" /></figure>\r\n<figure><img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/20170503_115353-n7z5l5vgozbsht3p62pu9ufoaty1cqskmoiilel6zk.jpg" alt="The TestBed''s Setup" /></figure>\r\n<figure><img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/20170503_115311-n7z5kycr6b1hwxemdzgtpwbzjqz3n5ypxnamr6wcdc.jpg" alt="The TestBed''s Setup" /></figure>\r\n<figure><img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/20170503_115343-n7z5l31y4h7xiz7smjhykd5aiobxpnhdmak25kpdi8.jpg" alt="The TestBed''s Setup" /></figure>\r\n<h3><strong>What hardware do we have ?</strong></h3>\r\nThe TestBed is composed of :\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>10 USRP Boards</li>\r\n 	<li>a monitor</li>\r\n 	<li>two Windows stations and to finish a Linux station</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n8 of them are a N210 Model\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="alignnone" width="350"]<img src="https://www.ettus.com/content/images/prod_un210-kit_01_lg.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="191" /> N210 USRP[/caption]\r\n\r\n2 of them are a E110 model\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="alignnone" width="347"]<img src="http://www.cqdx.ru/ham/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/prod_ue110-kit_01_md.jpg" alt="" width="347" height="286" /> E110 USRP[/caption]\r\n\r\nThe last USRP is a B210 model\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/wordpress/index.php/testbed/how-it-works/">\r\nClick here\r\n</a>', 'TestBed', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '727-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-11 14:18:17', '2017-05-11 12:18:17', '', 727, 'http://localhost/wordpress/index.php/2017/05/11/727-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
